+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CgjyeXpW9gupbQMNqC5WEL","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've successfully read all files in the src/ directory. Here's a comprehensive overview of the codebase structure:\n\n## Codebase Structure Summary\n\n### File Listing:\n1. `/workspace/src/db/connection.ts` - Database initialization\n2. `/workspace/src/db/queries.ts` - Database queries\n3. `/workspace/src/models/invoice.ts` - TypeScript interfaces\n4. `/workspace/src/server.ts` - Express server setup\n5. `/workspace/src/services/billing.ts` - Billing calculations\n6. `/workspace/src/services/reporting.ts` - Reporting functions\n7. `/workspace/src/utils/dates.ts` - Date utilities\n8. `/workspace/src/utils/format.ts` - Formatting utilities\n\n---\n\n## Complete File Contents:\n\n### 1. `/workspace/src/db/connection.ts`\nInitializes a SQLite database using better-sqlite3 with two tables:\n- `invoices` table with fields for customer_id, date, subtotal, discount_rate, tax_rate, total, and status\n- `line_items` table with description, quantity, unit_price, and foreign key to invoices\n\n### 2. `/workspace/src/db/queries.ts`\nDatabase query functions:\n- `getInvoicesByDateRange()` - Retrieve invoices within a date range\n- `getInvoiceById()` - Get single invoice with line items\n- `createInvoice()` - Create new invoice with line items\n- `getInvoicesByCustomer()` - Get all invoices for a customer\n\n### 3. `/workspace/src/models/invoice.ts`\nTypeScript interfaces defining:\n- `LineItem` - Invoice line item\n- `Invoice` - Main invoice data structure\n- `InvoiceCreateInput` - Input data for creating invoices\n- `InvoiceSummary` - Monthly revenue summary\n- `CustomerReport` - Customer billing report\n\n### 4. `/workspace/src/server.ts`\nExpress server with 5 endpoints:\n- `GET /invoices` - List invoices by date range\n- `GET /invoices/:id` - Get invoice by ID\n- `POST /invoices` - Create new invoice\n- `GET /reports/monthly` - Monthly revenue report\n- `GET /reports/customer/:id` - Customer report\n\n### 5. `/workspace/src/services/billing.ts`\nBilling calculation functions:\n- `calculateInvoiceTotal()` - Calculates total: subtotal × (1 - discountRate) × (1 + taxRate)\n- `applyDiscount()` - Apply discount to subtotal\n- `calculateSubtotal()` - Calculate subtotal from line items\n- `generateInvoice()` - Main function to generate and persist invoices\n\n### 6. `/workspace/src/services/reporting.ts`\nReporting functions:\n- `getMonthlyReport()` - Generate monthly revenue report for a year\n- `getCustomerReport()` - Generate customer billing report with statistics\n- `getRevenueByPeriod()` - Get revenue totals for a date period\n\n### 7. `/workspace/src/utils/dates.ts`\nDate utility functions:\n- `formatDate()` - Convert Date to ISO string (YYYY-MM-DD)\n- `parseDate()` - Parse ISO date string to Date object\n- `getMonthRange()` - Get start and end dates for a month\n- `isDateInRange()` - Check if date falls within range\n- **NOTE:** Contains TODO comment about timezone fix\n\n### 8. `/workspace/src/utils/format.ts`\nFormatting utilities:\n- `formatCurrency()` - Format number as currency ($X,XXX.XX)\n- `formatPercentage()` - Format rate as percentage (XX.X%)\n- `calculateTax()` - Legacy function with **BUG**: applies rate as whole number instead of decimal (e.g., calculateTax(100, 0.08) returns 800 instead of 8)\n\n---\n\n## Key Observations:\n\n**Architecture:** Clean microservice for invoicing with separation of concerns - database layer, service layer, utilities, and Express API endpoints.\n\n**Known Issues:**\n1. Timezone handling TODO in `/workspace/src/utils/dates.ts`\n2. Bug in `calculateTax()` function in `/workspace/src/utils/format.ts` - applies rate as whole number instead of decimal\n\n**Dependencies:** better-sqlite3, express"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ab2aa4a (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 18091\ntool_uses: 9\ndur